    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="Shell变量"><a href="#Shell变量" class="headerlink" title="Shell变量"></a>Shell变量</h2><h5 id="变量定义格式："><a href="#变量定义格式：" class="headerlink" title="变量定义格式："></a>变量定义格式：</h5><p>1.变量名和等号之间不能有空格</p><p>2.只能使用英文字母，数字和下划线，不能以数字开头</p><p>3.中间不能有空格，可以使用下划线</p><p>4.不能使用标点符号</p><p>5.不能使用bash的关键字（help命令查看保留关键字）</p><p>正确的命名：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">RUNOOB</span><br><span class="line">LD_LIBRARY_PATH</span><br><span class="line">_var</span><br><span class="line">var2</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>错误的命名：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">?var=123   </span><br><span class="line">user*name=runoob</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#使用了标点符号</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="使用变量："><a href="#使用变量：" class="headerlink" title="使用变量："></a>使用变量：</h5><p>使用定义的变量，在变量名面前加美元符号($)</p><p>使用语法：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">your_name=&quot;qinjx&quot;</span><br><span class="line">echo $your_name</span><br><span class="line">echo $&#123;your_name&#125;  #变量名外面的花括号是可选的，加不加都行，加花括号是为了帮助解释器识别变量的边界，加花括号是一个好习惯。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p> 已定义的变量，可以被重新定义 </p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">your_name=<span class="string">&#x27;tom&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">your_name=<span class="string">&#x27;alibaba&#x27;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="只读变量："><a href="#只读变量：" class="headerlink" title="只读变量："></a>只读变量：</h5><p>使用readonly命令定义变量为只读变量</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">语法：<span class="built_in">readonly</span> 变量名</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="删除变量："><a href="#删除变量：" class="headerlink" title="删除变量："></a>删除变量：</h5><p>使用unset命令删除变量</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">语法：<span class="built_in">unset</span> 变量名</span><br><span class="line">myname=<span class="string">&#x27;hjl&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">unset</span> myname</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="variable">$myname</span></span><br><span class="line">输出结果：</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="变量类型："><a href="#变量类型：" class="headerlink" title="变量类型："></a>变量类型：</h5><p>（1）局部变量：局部变量在脚本中定义，只能在当前shell中使用有效，其他脚本无法调用</p><p>（2）环境变量：所有程序都可以使用，包括shell启动的脚本</p><p>（3）shell变量：shell变量中有一部分是环境变量，有一部分是局部变量，这些变量保证了shell的正常运行 </p><h2 id="Shell字符串"><a href="#Shell字符串" class="headerlink" title="Shell字符串"></a>Shell字符串</h2><p>  字符串可以用单引号，也可以用双引号，也可以不用引号 。</p><h5 id="单引号："><a href="#单引号：" class="headerlink" title="单引号："></a>单引号：</h5><p>单引号里的字符串会原样输出</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">str=<span class="string">&#x27;this is a str&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="variable">$str</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">输出结果：</span><br><span class="line">this is my name</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p> 单引号字符串中的变量是无效的 </p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">myname=<span class="string">&#x27;hjl&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">&#x27;this is my name $hjl&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">输出结果：</span><br><span class="line">this is my name <span class="variable">$hjl</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="双引号："><a href="#双引号：" class="headerlink" title="双引号："></a>双引号：</h5><p>输出内容：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">&quot;this is my name&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">输出结果：</span><br><span class="line">this is my name</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p> 双引号里可以有变量 </p><p> 双引号里可以出现转义字符 </p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">str=<span class="string">&#x27;hello world&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">&quot;print\&quot;<span class="variable">$str</span>\&quot;!&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">输出结果：</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span><span class="string">&quot;hello world&quot;</span>!</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="转义字符"><a href="#转义字符" class="headerlink" title="转义字符"></a>转义字符</h5><p>所有的<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/ASCII%E7%A0%81">ASCII码</a>都可以用“\”加数字（一般是8进制数字）来表示。而<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/C/7252092">C</a>中定义了一些字母前加”&quot;来表示常见的那些不能显示的ASCII字符，如\0,\t,\n等，就称为转义字符，因为后面的<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6/4768913">字符</a>，都不是它本来的ASCII字符意思了 。</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
